<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 02:04:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>定制饮料可以提供太空营养</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/tailored-drinks-could-provide-space-nutrition</link><description>研究人员开发出了可定制的 omega-3 纳米乳液饮料，以保护宇航员的骨骼和肌肉免受太空辐射。 [&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/tailored-drinks-could-provide-space-nutrition.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 02:04:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/tailored-drinks-could-provide-space-nutrition</guid></item><item><title>一种名为萨拉卡替尼（saracatinib）的抗癌药物刚刚让阿尔茨海默病小鼠恢复了衰竭的大脑突触——记忆也随之恢复</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/a-cancer-drug-called-saracatinib-just-switched-failing-brain-synapses-back-on-in-alzheimers-mice-memory-returned-with-them</link><description>当耶鲁大学的研究人员给大脑已经受到类似阿尔茨海默病的损伤的老老鼠服用一种被搁置的癌症药物时，这些动物又开始记忆了。原本安静的突触突然恢复了生机。标志着健康大脑连接的蛋白质攀升至正常水平。当药物被取消后，认知能力的提高就被保留下来了。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-cancer-drug-called-saracatinib-just-switched-failing-brain-synapses-back-on-in-alzheimers-mice-memory-returned-with-them.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 01:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/a-cancer-drug-called-saracatinib-just-switched-failing-brain-synapses-back-on-in-alzheimers-mice-memory-returned-with-them</guid></item><item><title>机械负荷抑制小鼠和人类心脏中的癌症生长</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mechanical-load-inhibits-cancer-growth-in-mouse-and-human-hearts</link><description>心脏的持续跳动可能会积极抑制心脏组织中的肿瘤生长，这是一种新的研究&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/mechanical-load-inhibits-cancer-growth-in-mouse-and-human-hearts2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 01:34:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/mechanical-load-inhibits-cancer-growth-in-mouse-and-human-hearts</guid></item><item><title>鸽子大脑中磁诱导神经元活动的全局筛选</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/a-global-screen-for-magnetically-induced-neuronal-activity-in-the-pigeon-brain</link><description>如果你读到的每一篇科学论文都只是一部更长、更混乱、更复杂的电影的“精彩片段”怎么办？你看到了突破，但你永远看不到数百小时的镜头显示什么不起作用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/a-global-screen-for-magnetically-induced-neuronal-activity-in-the-pigeon-brain2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 01:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/a-global-screen-for-magnetically-induced-neuronal-activity-in-the-pigeon-brain</guid></item><item><title>大型语言模型在医生推理任务中的表现</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/performance-of-a-large-language-model-on-the-reasoning-tasks-of-a-physician</link><description>如果你读到的每一篇科学论文都只是一部更长、更混乱、更复杂的电影的“精彩片段”怎么办？你看到了突破，但你永远看不到数百小时的镜头显示什么不起作用。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/performance-of-a-large-language-model-on-the-reasoning-tasks-of-a-physician2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 01:04:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/performance-of-a-large-language-model-on-the-reasoning-tasks-of-a-physician</guid></item><item><title>雇用未来学家？大多数领导团队忽视的危险信号</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/hiring-a-futurist-the-red-flag-most-leadership-teams-miss</link><description>当领导团队聘请未来学家来为他们思考未来时，聘用本身就是失败。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/hiring-a-futurist-the-red-flag-most-leadership-teams-miss.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 00:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/hiring-a-futurist-the-red-flag-most-leadership-teams-miss</guid></item><item><title>OpenAI 击败埃隆·马斯克诉讼，扫清 IPO 障碍</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/openai-defeats-elon-musks-lawsuit-removes-obstacle-to-ipo</link><description>美国陪审团裁定 OpenAI 无需因涉嫌偏离造福人类的初衷而对世界首富承担责任。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/openai-defeats-elon-musks-lawsuit-removes-obstacle-to-ipo.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 00:34:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/openai-defeats-elon-musks-lawsuit-removes-obstacle-to-ipo</guid></item><item><title>利用人工智能和增强现实技术检测和管理转移性癌症（综述）</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/metastatic-cancer-detection-and-management-with-artificial-intelligence-and-augmented-reality-review</link><description>转移性癌症仍然是一个重大的全球健康挑战，由于发现较晚、治疗耐药和播散性疾病的复杂性，导致大部分癌症相关死亡。人工智能 (AI) 和增强现实 (AR) 的最新进展正在改变转移性癌症检测和管理的格局。人工智能驱动的工具，包括放射组学、深度学习模型和预测分析，通过整合多模式临床、影像和分子数据，增强转移性病变的早期识别，提高诊断准确性，并支持个性化治疗策略。与此同时，AR技术越来越多地应用于图像引导手术、实时肿瘤可视化和患者教育，从而实现更精准的干预和改善临床决策。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/metastatic-cancer-detection-and-management-with-artificial-intelligence-and-augmented-reality-review.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 00:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/metastatic-cancer-detection-and-management-with-artificial-intelligence-and-augmented-reality-review</guid></item><item><title>常见的哮喘药物可能会关闭与免疫治疗耐药相关的肿瘤“开关”</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/common-asthma-drug-may-turn-off-tumor-switch-tied-to-immunotherapy-resistance</link><description>西北医学的一项新研究报告称，一种广泛用于治疗哮喘和过敏的药物也可能有助于对抗侵袭性癌症，该研究揭示了肿瘤如何劫持常见的白细胞来逃避免疫治疗。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/common-asthma-drug-may-turn-off-tumor-switch-tied-to-immunotherapy-resistance.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 20 May 2026 00:04:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/common-asthma-drug-may-turn-off-tumor-switch-tied-to-immunotherapy-resistance</guid></item><item><title>仔细的结晶为晶体管解锁了有序的钙钛矿层</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/careful-crystallization-unlocks-well-ordered-perovskite-layers-for-transistors</link><description>钙钛矿是一类具有独特晶体结构的材料，适合制造太阳能电池、发光二极管和晶体管等应用。然而，薄层中的分子通常无法正确排列，因为该过程进行得太快。现在，由马克斯·普朗克聚合物研究所的 Tomasz Marszalek 领导的国际研究小组开发了一种控制低成本溶液加工的新方法，从而改善有序钙钛矿层的形成并使其在光电器件中得到更广泛的应用。他们的论文是&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/careful-crystallization-unlocks-well-ordered-perovskite-layers-for-transistors.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 19 May 2026 23:49:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/05/careful-crystallization-unlocks-well-ordered-perovskite-layers-for-transistors</guid></item></channel></rss>